      • withDeadline

        public static String[] withDeadline(String s1,
                                    String[] ss,
                                    float deadline,
                                    AlgMap.Alg alg,
                                    Object... args)
        Parameters:

        deadline - the min/max rank of the elements in the array which is returned
        algInstance - an instance of Algorithm that will be used to perform the comparison
        alg - an instance of AlgMap.Alg. It must refer to the same algorithm referred by algInstance. Check AlgMap
        Returns:
        a sorted String[] containing at most n elements with rank >= deadline if Utils.biggerIsBetter(alg) is true, only elements with rank <= deadline if Utils.biggerIsBetter(alg) is false
